claim.claim-text:
6. A magnetic disk drive comprising: 
a magnetic disk; 
disk driving means for driving the magnetic disk; 
a magnetic head provided with a reproducing head and a recording head; and 
means for positioning the magnetic head with respect to the magnetic disk, 
wherein the magnetic disk is one provided with recording and soft magnetic layers, and designed for perpendicular magnetic recording, and the magnetic head is one specified in claim 1.
